  <brief_title>Secondary Adjuvant Long Term Study With Arimidex</brief_title>
  <acronym>SALSA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Open, Multicentre Phase III-study to Assess the Efficacy of Secondary Adjuvant Endocrine Anastrozole Therapy for 2 Further Yrs vs 5 Further Yrs in Patients With HR +ve Breast Cancer After 5-yr Primary Adjuvant Endocrine Therapy</official_title>
